quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  45,33,"Feeñaniɓe boneeji golle mum en nder aduna ummorde e keefaraagu e goopi, lepte ɗeɓe njalkitatno tellii e mum en ɗeɓe njeertinteno e mum."
  45,34,"Alla daalaniɓe: hannde Min acca on e yiite hono no yejjatirɗon ñalngu mon hannde ngu, on keblanaani ngu iimaan e golle lobbe, ko yiite woni ñiiɓirde, on ngalah balla diiwanoowo mon leɓte."
  45,35,"Leɓte ɗe ɗe lepteɗon sabu ko njaggirno ɗon aayeeje Alla ɗe saboote e jalkitde, nguurndam aduna ɗam hodiri mon dakamme e tuuyooji majjam, hannde ɓe heeferɓe jalkitatnooɓe aayeeje Alla njaltatah yiite, ɓe keddato e henge haa pooma, ɓe nduttetaake e nguurndam aduna haa ɓe ngolla golle lobbe, Joomi mum en weletaake ɓe."
  45,36,"Ko Alla tan woodani jettoode, Jom kammuuji e leydi, Jom denndaangal tagu."
  45,37,"Ina woodani Mbo teddungal e manngu nder kammuuji e leydi, kanko woni poolɗo mbo gooto foolatah, nyeenya e tagu makko e hoddira makko e jiilgol makko e sariya makko."
  46,1,"Haa, Miim. Yewtere fii sugu ɗee kalfe yawtiino ka simoore Al baqarah."
  46,2,"Jippagol Alqur'aana, ko immorde ka Allah, hay foolondirtah e Makko, Ñeeñuɗo e tagu Mun e kattal Mun e toppitagol e sariya Mun."
  46,3,"Men tagiraali kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, fii fijindaaru; ko Men tagiri ɗin fow, ko hoore goonga e ñeeñe yottiiɗe: wano fii no jeyaaɓe ɓen anndira ɗin, woodeede Mo, ɓe rewa Mo Kanko tun, hara ɓe kafidaali Mo e huunde, e no ɓe tottira paandale lontineede ɓe nden ka leydi, haa e caatal happaangal, ngal Allah tun anndi fii mun. Yedduɓe Allah ɓen non, ko ɓe ɗuurniiɓe e kon ko ɓe jertinaara ka Deftere Allah, ɓe haajaaka e ɗum."
  46,4,"An Nulaaɗo, maakan ɓee sirkooɓe ɗuurniiɓe e goonga: yeetee lam fii sanamuuji mon ɗi rewoton accon Allah ɗin, ko honɗum e geɗe ɗi tagi e leydi ndin? Hara ko fello? Kaa ko ilol? Kaa hara hiɗi kafidi e Allah ka tagugol kammuuli ɗin? Awa addanee lam Deftere jipporiinde ka Allah, ado ndee Alqur'aanaare, maa batte ganndal ko adinooɓe acii, si wonii ko on goonguɓe e ko nodditorton, wonnde sanamuuji mon ɗin hino hanndi e reweede!"
  46,5,"Alaa ɓurɗo majjude, wa on rewuɗo ko wanaa Allah, sanamu ko jaabotaako mo haa Darngal daroo! Hara non, ɗin sanamuuji, ko welsindiiɗi e ko ɓe rewata ɗin kon, wanaa fii ɗi nafa ɓe maa ɗi lorra ɓe."